                            <small>Availability: ${data.systemStats.availability.toFixed(2)}% | MTBF: ${formatHHMMSS(data.systemStats.mtbf_min)} | MTTR: ${formatHHMMSS(data.systemStats.mttr_min)}</small>
                        </div>
